y":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5a86eda15f51414a26158b23625ef6bc82be37","tid":1699800,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8d4995f0ffe24864f42c9beb9e1ff17e4bd715f","tid":1699800,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f828bbba4057cb3fbd08d4f9318de941fae5d17","tid":1699800,"uid":291656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2270407486f6acfae09ed3252d08207754a340f","tid":1699800,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"講撚左好耐啦<br />\n每次都有左膠次次阻撚住晒<br />\n話咩民意逆轉<br />\n行動升級會嚇走和理非<br />\n算 我忍<br />\n<br />\n真正落場打果陣<br />\n就整rb扔石仔<br />\n得閒就屌狗嗌口號<br />\n明明佔據優勢就唔攻只守<br />\n結果班狗開始有增緩就邊打邊退<br />\n最撚on9嘅係<br />\n千尻幾人第一時間唔係同班狗搏命<br />\n而係起勢咁逃跑<br />\n對面頂多咪一百隻<br />\n個個都係貪生怕死同羊群心理<br />\n<br />\n咁樣打仗點樣贏<br />\n勇武都好打有限<br />\n更何況仲要係少數？<br />\n<br />\n「攻擊就係最好嘅防禦」<br />\n只要攻破班狗嘅第一條防線<br />\n士氣嗰啲肯定咩都番晒黎<br />\n有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n到時個氣勢一定好過而家咁撚樣<br />\n<br />\n家下就係攻又攻唔破<br />\n守又守唔住<br />\n叫你地改下戰略又話分化又話冇上過前線乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n我屌如果你本身條橋係掂我地就唔洗講咁撚多野啦"},{"pid":"0bf98f3526b4f490accf26e3c29b8523c5ae07ac","tid":1699800,"uid":78250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"我地係咪要考慮改變模式 由六日嘅抗爭活動轉至平日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699811</a><br />\n大家一齊brainstorm下<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c129a71aae86708cca4387623301202448ed56","tid":1699800,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:29:27.000Z","ms